  "info": {
    "name": "Servisni Centar Gitara API 3",
    "description": "Manual API test collection for the Servisni Centar Gitara ASP.NET Core MVC/API project. All requests use {{baseUrl}}. Protected routes use ASP.NET Core Identity cookie authentication. In Postman keep Auth Type = No Auth and set the collection variable identityCookie CURRENT VALUE to the value of the .AspNetCore.Identity.Application cookie copied from the browser after login. A collection pre-request script injects Cookie: .AspNetCore.Identity.Application={{identityCookie}} before every request. If you receive 401, the cookie is missing/expired/wrong host. If you receive 403, the cookie works but the user does not have the required role.",
